## addDeliveryContentIfNonExistentAction variable

Adds this content item to the store only if the item does not exist, yet. If the item does not exist, this triggers a [addDeliveryContentAction](./redux-feature-delivery-content.adddeliverycontentaction.md)<!-- -->.

<b>Signature:</b>

```typescript
addDeliveryContentIfNonExistentAction: UnaryFunction<ContentItemWithLayout, AddDeliveryContentIfNonExistentAction>
```
